1
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,280
Go.

2
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,160
Yes, Father.

3
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,200
Hmph.

4
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,039
Hu Linglong.

5
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,600
Since you're my junior,

6
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,280
I didn't take it completely seriously.

7
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,640
That's why I made a mistake.

8
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:42,160
Let's say I let you win this round.

9
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:42,840
After this,

10
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,600
I won't hold back anymore.

11
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,360
Let's continue.

12
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:49,560
Fragrance reaches the clouds,

13
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,920
The cup holds a whole world.

14
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,840
The second round

15
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,680
will be

16
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,880
Savoring Fragrance.

17
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,920
We will serve both of you

18
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:02,360
an identical cup of tea.

19
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:05,600
Whoever can correctly identify

20
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:09,880
the tea leaves and the water used for brewing faster

21
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,800
will be the winner.

22
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,240
What a strange smell.

23
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:39,960
Wait.

24
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:41,600
You...

25
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,600
What's wrong?

26
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:45,440
I've lost my sense of smell.

27
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,320
What's going on here?

28
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,160
Hu Linglong,

29
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,620
you think you can fight us?

30
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:00,010
Could it be that the tea was tampered with?

31
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,480
Young Master,

32
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,680
what are you doing?

33
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,320
Look at this,

34
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:06,400
the tea is sitting right here.

35
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,760
Why hasn't it been served yet?

36
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:08,960
It's your turn to ask me? Quick, quick.

37
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,600
Hurry up.

38
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,660
Yes, Young Master.

39
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,600
Clan Elder,

40
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,960
I have my answer.

41
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:29,840
Wenyi,

42
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,960
tell us what it is.

43
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,400
The tea soup is bright green and clear,

44
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,079
and the aroma is high and refreshing.

45
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:39,640
The tea used

46
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:42,560
should be Songluo tea from Xiuning.

47
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,079
It was picked around Guyu,

48
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:46,200
and roasted and rolled twice.

49
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:47,200
Wenyi,

50
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,600
what you said is absolutely correct.

51
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,600
Not bad.

52
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,240
Wenyi,

53
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,240
what about the water?

54
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,400
Where does it come from?

55
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,280
As for the water,

56
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,240
let Hu Linglong answer.

57
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,480
If she can answer it,

58
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:08,680
I will willingly admit defeat

59
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:10,680
and acknowledge her as the head of the family.

60
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,800
This way,

61
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:14,000
others won't say I'm bullying a junior

62
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,360
and gossip about me.

63
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,160
Linglong,

64
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,320
since Uncle Hu

65
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:22,200
is willing to be so generous,

66
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,920
tell us

67
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,760
where the water in this tea

68
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,240
comes from.

69
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,720
If you are right,

70
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:31,000
you will immediately become the head of the family.

71
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,920
Clan...

72
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,800
Clan Elder.

73
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,000
I...

74
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,080
I can't smell anything.

75
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,400
Hahaha.

76
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,960
In that case,

77
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:44,080
let Wenyi answer.

78
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:46,280
To answer the elder,

79
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,240
the water in this tea

80
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,360
is pure and clear.

81
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,240
Besides the taste of tea,

82
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,560
it also has the fragrance of grass and wood.

83
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,280
It must be the morning dew

84
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:54,720
collected from the leaves in the tea garden that day.

85
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,880
Everything Wenyi said is correct.

86
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,480
In the second round,

87
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:00,200
Hu Wenyi wins.

88
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,160
Good.

89
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,560
Just you wait.

90
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,920
Hahaha.

91
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,120
Change the tea sets.

92
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,720
As the saying goes in the tea ceremony,

93
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,160
observe its color,

94
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,400
smell its fragrance.

95
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,080
A bowl of good tea

96
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:26,400
shows not only the skill

97
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,640
but also the craftsmanship.

98
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,480
Therefore, in this third round,

99
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,210
we will compete on the tea soup.

100
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,800
There is definitely something wrong with this tea.

101
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,320
Why am I dizzy?

102
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,960
Are you okay?

103
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:39,640
I...

104
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,320
I don't feel well.

105
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,560
Give my body back to me.

106
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,640
I will continue the tea competition.

107
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,400
How about it?

108
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,080
Between the two of you,

109
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,409
whoever brews a tea soup

110
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:52,800
with perfect color, aroma, and taste

111
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:54,760
will be the winner.

112
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:56,880
Next,

113
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,860
the two of you will take turns.

114
00:05:59,159 --> 00:06:01,290
You have the time of one incense stick.

115
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,480
Who goes first?

116
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,400
If I give the body back so easily,

117
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,840
won't I go back to that illusion again?

118
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,800
In your current state,

119
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,600
how can you win against Hu Wenyi?

120
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,520
I'll go first.

121
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,780
Please light the incense.

122
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,360
The tea I chose

123
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:44,200
is the premium Fulu tea from Fufeng.

124
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,400
It is the best among the Fulu teas.

125
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:47,800
The water used for brewing the tea

126
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,760
is taken from a clear mountain spring.

127
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,920
It is sifted and filtered three times,

128
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,200
pure and flawless.

129
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,840
The finest Fulu tea soup

130
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,300
is green and translucent.

131
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:58,000
Like the tender leaves of early spring,

132
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,880
the color of jade dew can be seen at the bottom of the cup.

133
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:00,840
As the saying goes,

134
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,760
"When the golden wind meets the jade dew,

135
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,520
spring can be hidden in a cup."

136
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,200
Good.

137
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,760
Hu Linglong,

138
00:07:08,760 --> 00:07:10,000
it's your turn.

139
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,760
If we fail,

140
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,960
neither of us will have a good end.

141
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,680
For a normal person,

142
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,760
having no sense of smell is absolutely impossible.

143
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:23,080
But for me, it's just an ordinary thing.

144
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:29,080
I should have a way to win this competition.

145
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:31,120
Then we can take our time to plan.

146
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,240
Did you hear me?

147
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,200
Hey.

148
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,840
Alright.

149
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,080
I...

150
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:53,159
I really came back.

151
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,520
Humph.

152
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,800
Deliberately mystifying.

153
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,800
Even if there's no chance of winning,

154
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,800
this competition,

155
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,060
I will fight to the end.

156
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,560
Elder.

157
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,920
The tea I chose

158
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,440
is produced in Likou,

159
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,840
selected from Keemun black tea,

160
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,770
and is the finest Congou black tea.

161
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,120
The water used is

162
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,760
ordinary spring water.

163
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,280
Hmph.

164
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,680
Ordinary spring water.

165
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:19,760
Father.

166
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:22,320
I suddenly lost my sense of smell a few days ago.

167
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:24,080
I can't smell anything now.

168
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:26,010
How can I learn to make tea from you?

169
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,280
Qingyun.

170
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,040
Today, I will teach you a method

171
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,600
to make good tea

172
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,919
without relying on your sense of smell.

173
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,000
Really?

174
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,840
It's my first time hearing this.

175
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,960
The tea brewed this way

176
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:42,120
is a hundred times better than ordinary tea.

177
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,320
I don't believe it.

178
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,680
You don't believe me?

179
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,920
Then I'll show you.

180
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:48,000
Since you can't rely on your sense of smell,

181
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,060
you must maximize your other senses.

182
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,840
Throughout the brewing process,

183
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,240
keep the lid off the bowl,

184
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,690
and your eyes on the tea.

185
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,520
Hahaha.

186
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,440
Elder,

187
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,880
she can't even brew

188
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:16,440
the most basic clear tea.

189
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:20,280
And the tea smells completely bland.

190
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,400
I won't even taste this tea.

191
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:23,440
Wait.

192
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,600
Elder,

193
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,280
you can

194
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:30,160
announce my victory.

195
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,080
Hahaha.

196
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,040
Listen with your ears

197
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,900
to understand the tea's essence.

198
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,320
Touch the cup with your hands

199
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,920
to determine the timing.

200
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,400
Look at this.

201
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,800
Amber Golden Tea.

202
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,960
So beautiful.

203
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:20,240
Even among

204
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,760
the past heads of our Hu family,

205
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,320
few have successfully brewed this.

206
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:27,920
Wow.

207
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,360
You're amazing, Father.

208
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,680
I remember.

209
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,530
The last time I saw this,

210
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:41,160
it seemed to be made by her father, Wenzhong.

211
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,080
Ah.

212
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,000
I announce that

213
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,080
in the third round,

214
00:11:11,640 --> 00:11:12,920
Hu Linglong wins.

215
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,200
I object.

216
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,490
With just her, Hu Linglong,

217
00:11:25,640 --> 00:11:28,040
she could never brew the Amber Golden Tea.

218
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:29,480
She must have cheated.

219
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,720
Please, Elder.

220
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,000
I want to compete with her again.

221
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:34,920
Hu Wenyi.

222
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,320
You have no proof.

223
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,960
Why are you framing my Long'er?

224
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:38,840
Hu Wenyi.

225
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,480
So you mean that

226
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,480
in front of everyone,

227
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,200
the Elder intentionally favored me?

228
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,000
Hu Wenyi.

229
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:46,440
If you are a sore loser,

230
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,320
just say so.

231
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,600
Elder.

232
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,920
If the position of family head

233
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,650
is handed over to a little girl,

234
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,960
the century-old foundation of the Hu family...

235
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,800
I'm afraid in the end,

236
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:57,360
all the wealth will be lost and you'll be ruined.

237
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,160
Hu Wenyi,

238
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,320
how could you say that?

239
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,040
The Hu family

240
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:04,720
has always used tea competitions to decide the winner

241
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,760
and determine

242
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,240
who will succeed.

243
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,200
As a clan elder,

244
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,640
how can I in front of everyone

245
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,720
easily go back on my word

246
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,080
and favor you?

247
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:15,680
Humph.

248
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,800
This is outrageous.

249
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,320
I announce that

250
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,970
the tea competition

251
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:35,240
is over.

252
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:41,800
Everyone,

253
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:42,880
please follow me

254
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:44,200
to the front hall.

255
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:49,400
Mother.

256
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,280
Humph.

257
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:08,680
Yamamoto-san,

258
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,720
everything has been investigated.

259
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,400
That greedy loser Hu Wenyi

260
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,880
didn't become the head of the family.

261
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:14,410
The black tea secret recipe

262
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,640
won't be easy to get, I'm afraid.

263
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,560
I have plenty of ways

264
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,400
to get this recipe.
